Heat sausage and sauce in small saucepan over low heat until hot. Meanwhile, cut polenta into 12 slices. In 12-inch skillet heat olive oil over medium heat until hot. Add polenta slices. Cook 6 to 7 minutes or until light golden brown, turning once. To serve, place 3 slices on serving plate, top with 1/4 of the sausage mixture. Sprinkle with parsley. Serve immediately.